  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Anime, Netflix, and Movies with your Favorite Twitch Streamers</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.poster.avif?t=1630543896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.webm?t=1630543896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.mp4?t=1630543896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tenami is the premier watch party platform for Twitch.tv that allows users to watch content from Netflix, Crunchyroll, or YouTube to watch in sync with their live streams. When a streamer watches an anime, YouTube video, or movie through Tenami, viewers of their Twitch stream will be able to watch alongside them simply by joining their twitch stream.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Supported Platforms</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Netflix<br></li><li>Crunchyroll<br></li><li>YouTube<br></li><li>Twitch</li></ul><br>Want to watch with your close friends? That’s okay too! Create a private lobby and share the code to your friends so that you can watch together without having to leave the comfort of your home!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Anime, Netflix, and Movies with your Favorite Twitch Streamers</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.poster.avif?t=1630543896\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.webm?t=1630543896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414930/extras/ae9c577d2b7277fd8f5416e1ef7caadd.mp4?t=1630543896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tenami is the premier watch party platform for Twitch.tv that allows users to watch content from Netflix, Crunchyroll, or YouTube to watch in sync with their live streams. When a streamer watches an anime, YouTube video, or movie through Tenami, viewers of their Twitch stream will be able to watch alongside them simply by joining their twitch stream.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Supported Platforms</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Netflix<br></li><li>Crunchyroll<br></li><li>YouTube<br></li><li>Twitch</li></ul><br>Want to watch with your close friends? That’s okay too! Create a private lobby and share the code to your friends so that you can watch together without having to leave the comfort of your home!",
